{"tid":1266983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［救港] 登報不能停","createTime":"2019-06-29T16:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T18:13:05.000Z","uid":65196,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c398794f4791e7cb1d5728cc5da103d846ee3f2a","tid":1266983,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:48:57.000Z","msg":"認真登報其實策略正確，但唔需要咁多個國家<br />\n<br />\n我地可以做嘅係繼續集資，瘋狂登報，budget唔夠可以唔使落頭版，但真係要不斷咁繼續登報，尤其是係美國<br />\n<br />\n因為能夠真真正正幫到香港嘅，除咗香港人自己去不斷抗爭，就一定係《香港民主及人權法案》，我哋要持續將香港嘅狀況同政府嘅謊言更新比美國嘅人知、更新比美國嘅議員知！！我哋報道嘅每一個真相同公開信都係對港共政權同垃圾建制派最有力嘅攻擊！！！"},{"pid":"4042f86cf83a9873454d68c664786a1b1990999e","tid":1266983,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:49:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7996dd82f9c1af623badebc6aabd60d90b8949cd","tid":1266983,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:49:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28e7ed7d7e0cce1f4d6eae7053406b40da14b79e","tid":1266983,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:49:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b6072cebcd40aad1ff5c92b6e76efe456f1528c","tid":1266983,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:49:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94d87c8ca0a75a70089994ca7b0983db8d9d643f","tid":1266983,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:50:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46128debebfce848a62490c764d27af5f4f409e4","tid":1266983,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c1a7a389ec7e8b227561c3d5c32e6c232a2f1f8","tid":1266983,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:51:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0737815c45b6713ef8e91a5eb891c19fb7269a3","tid":1266983,"uid":23373,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:51:07.000Z","msg":"人地係你屋企痴張唔關自己事既海報<br />\n你都第一時間搣佢落黎<br />\n<br />\n一次係震撼,多次就係多餘"},{"